---
// ヒーロー セクション / Hero Section
---

<section class="hero" id="home">
  <div class="hero-content">
    <div class="hero-text">
      <h1 class="hero-title">文字で<br />心を編む</h1>
      <div class="line"></div>
      <!-- 自己紹介 / Introduction -->
      <p class="hero-subtitle">
        深みのある文学作品の創作に励む作家。ペンの先から生活の物語を紡ぎます。
      </p>
      <!-- CTA ボタン / Call to Action Buttons -->
      <div class="cta-buttons">
        <a
          href="https://x.com/iktahana"
          target="_blank"
          class="btn btn-secondary"
        >
          <img
            src="/social-icons/x.min.svg"
            alt="X"
			style="height: 20px;filter: invert(100%);"
          /> @iktahana
        </a>
        <a
          href="https://note.com/iktahana"
          target="_blank"
          class="btn btn-secondary"
        >
          <img
            src="/social-icons/note.min.svg"
            alt="Note"
            style="height: 30px;"
          />
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-image">
      <svg
        class="illustration"
        viewBox="0 0 300 400"
        xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
      >
        <rect
          x="30"
          y="50"
          width="240"
          height="300"
          fill="none"
          stroke="#2c2c2c"
          stroke-width="1.5"></rect>
        <circle
          cx="150"
          cy="90"
          r="30"
          fill="none"
          stroke="#2c2c2c"
          stroke-width="1.5"></circle>
        <path d="M 50 150 L 250 150" stroke="#2c2c2c" stroke-width="1"></path>
        <path d="M 50 170 L 250 170" stroke="#2c2c2c" stroke-width="1"></path>
        <path d="M 50 190 L 250 190" stroke="#2c2c2c" stroke-width="1"></path>
        <path d="M 50 210 L 250 210" stroke="#2c2c2c" stroke-width="1"></path>
        <path d="M 50 230 L 230 230" stroke="#2c2c2c" stroke-width="1"></path>
        <path d="M 50 250 L 200 250" stroke="#2c2c2c" stroke-width="1"></path>
        <path
          d="M 80 280 Q 150 300 220 290"
          stroke="#2c2c2c"
          stroke-width="1"
          fill="none"></path>
      </svg>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .cta-buttons .btn {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 0.6rem;
    line-height: 1;
  }

  .cta-buttons .btn img {
    display: block;
    height: 20px;
    width: auto;
  }
</style>
